# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Env files — never commit secrets / local keys.
# Exception: .env.production holds only the PUBLIC Clerk publishable key (baked
# into the browser bundle anyway), so it IS committed for reproducible builds.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production

